OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,FA #129 million growth deal for
OL,7,FCauseway Coast and Glens has been
OL,8,Fformally signed.
OL,10,FThe signing of the financial agreement
OL,11,Ftook place at North West Regional
OL,12,FCollege in Limavady on Wednesday.
OL,14,FIt represents a funding package of #36
OL,15,Fmillion from the UK Goverment, with
OL,16,Fthe same amount coming from the
OL,17,FExecutive.
OL,19,F#57 million will also be given from
OL,20,Fthe Causeway Coast and Glens Borough
OL,21,FCouncil and delivery partners.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
