PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1777539988
OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,FThe agreement hopes to boost
OL,7,Fproductivity, enhance innovation,
OL,8,Fsupport regeneration, and create new
OL,9,Fopportunities for residents,
OL,10,Fbusinesses and visitors in the area.
OL,12,FProjects in phase one represent 66% of
OL,13,Fthe overall investment.
OL,15,FUlster University's Centre for Food
OL,16,Fand Drug Discovery at Coleraine will
OL,17,Fbe part of phase one.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
