CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1777539988
OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,FColeraine Leisure & Wellbeing Centre,
OL,7,Fthe North West Regional College
OL,8,FFoodovation & Skills Centre, and
OL,9,Fregeneration programme for Dungiven
OL,10,Ftown centre are also included.
OL,12,FSecretary of State, Hilary Benn MP
OL,13,Fsaid: "The UK Government is committed
OL,14,Fto boosting prosperity and growth
OL,15,Facross Northern Ireland, and I'm
OL,16,Fdelighted to sign the Causeway Coast
OL,17,Fand Glens Growth deal, which will
OL,18,Funlock this region's potential by
OL,19,Fcreating opportunities and improving
OL,20,Ffacilities.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
