PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1777539988
OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,F"Our #36 million funding for this Deal
OL,7,Fwill support digital and innovation
OL,8,Fprojects, including the Centre for
OL,9,FDrug Discovery and Pharmaceutical
OL,10,FInnovation; the Foodovation and Skills
OL,11,FCentre; and the Business Innovation
OL,12,Fand Incubation Hub, all of which will
OL,13,Fbenefit the local community."
OL,15,FMinister for Finance, John O'Dowd MLA
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am delighted to sign the
OL,17,FGrowth Deal for Causeway Coast and
OL,18,FGlens which finalises the investment
OL,19,Fof #129 million in the region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@]O]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
