OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1777539988
OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,F"City and Growth Deals provide a
OL,7,Fproven framework for unlocking local
OL,8,Fpotential, supporting economic
OL,9,Frecovery through investment in jobs,
OL,10,Fskills, innovation and regeneration,
OL,11,Fand delivering lasting benefits for
OL,12,Fpeople and communities."
OL,14,FPrincipal and Chief and Executive of
OL,15,FNWRC, Leo Murphy said: "We are
OL,16,Fdelighted to host this landmark
OL,17,Fsigning event, a key moment in the
OL,18,FCauseway Coast and Glen Growth deal
OL,19,Fjourney that will have lasting
OL,20,Fbenefits for this region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@XO]wD@XOU
