OL,3,CCauseway Coast and Glens growth deal
OL,4,Csigned
OL,6,F"As a partner on both this deal, and
OL,7,Fthe Derry and Strabane City deal, NWRC
OL,8,Fis committed to bringing long term
OL,9,Fprosperity and real opportunity for
OL,10,Fthe people of this region."
OL,12,F"Our new Foodovation and Skills
OL,13,Fcentre will see a major refurbishment
OL,14,Fat Limavady campus and is expected to
OL,15,Fdeliver 75 new food sector jobs, train
OL,16,Fmore than 400 individuals each year
OL,17,Fand deliver 140 innovation projects
OL,18,Fannually."
